title: july 31: the greatest olympian
description:
In this episode of 365 days with mxmtoon, Maia talks about the record-breaking performance by Michael Phelps at the Olympics. After, she talks about the ill-fated Woodstock 50th reunion festival. Listen to this episode today and make sure you’re following along with the daily updates @365daysmxmtoon on all platforms.
